				As a 16th season Ranger, I have found this spell exceedingly useful in combat situations.  I usually stayed away from con yellow creatures unless I had a nice group.  Now, however, I can easily root them with this spell, and then pummel them with arrows and the burst of flame.  When it wears off, just cast again.  I know this has been emphasized a lot in these posts but I feel it cannot be emphasized enough.<BR>
